---
title: Herbed Chicken & Lemony Rice Bowls with Dark Meat Chicken, Tomato-Dill Relish & White Sauce
description: This Mediterranean-style dish is a veritable one-bowl feast that’s positively bursting with flavor. You’ll top a bed of fluffy lemon rice pilaf with garlic- and oregano-seasoned dark meat chicken, a refreshingly juicy tomato-dill salad, and a drizzle of tangy lemon sauce.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/66cca69fbced2ef414e81858-f6584b6e.jpeg
